  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to sign arbitrary messages so that Dapps can be supplied additional, non-critical data.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Dapps often require certain arbitrary data from users to enhance the UX or add additional novel functionality to the dapp.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nDapp will request account data from the user, user will then sign access to the dapp.\r\n\r\nIn this request, the dapp could request a user's name, preferred theme settings or supplying user data that should not be stored or transferred on chain or permanently.\r\n\r\nuPort as example allows the sending of user profile data from the user device to the Dapp via a messaging server.\r\n",
